commitResults.messageTitle: Make Interviewee use javafx properties so they are Observable (#80)
commitResults.messageBody:
By using an extractor in the IntervieweeLists' ObservableList,
the mutable Properties of an Interviewee (name, alias, resume and
transcript) have their changes tracked by the ListView as well

Add name and alias editing capabilities to IntervieweeList
IntervieweeList now allows user to edit interviewees' names, and
will automatically update the identifiers to remove old aliases and
names
